<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="56883" type="habitat">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="56883">Habitat</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="56883">We collected specimens in emergence traps spanned over littoral portions of small streams, on hygropetric rocks and along small rivulets. The species is generally found in banks of streams, ponds, lakes, freshwater marshlands and in association with waterfalls. It is also found in substrates that are muddy or sandy.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
